# Hospital Management System — Comprehensive API Testing Plan

## Status: IMPLEMENTED

## 1. Executive Summary

This plan covers **all 60+ API endpoints** across 12 domain areas. The existing test suite has **5 test files** with 15 tests covering auth, clinical workflow, security hardening, module boundaries, and security config defaults. We need to add comprehensive integration tests for **8 untested domains** plus edge-case coverage for the 3 already-tested domains.

---

## 2. Current Test Coverage Analysis

| Test File | Tests | Coverage Area |
|-----------|-------|---------------|
| `AuthenticationIntegrationTest` | 3 | Login, bad credentials, token refresh |
| `ClinicalWorkflowIntegrationTest` | 7 | Booking, check-in, medical record, patient history |
| `SecurityHardeningIntegrationTest` | 7 | Auth envelopes, CORS, expired tokens |
| `ModuleBoundaryTest` | 2 | Module dependency graph |
| `SecurityConfigurationDefaultsTest` | 2 | Config secrets validation |

### Gaps Identified
- ❌ **Patient Auth** (claim, login, refresh, logout)
- ❌ **Patient Portal** (overview, appointments, lab results, messages, profile)
- ❌ **Admin Users** (CRUD, activate/deactivate, role change)
- ❌ **Admin Departments** (CRUD, doctor assignment)
- ❌ **Admin Rooms** (CRUD, status)
- ❌ **Admin Schedule/Slots/Closures** (templates, time slots)
- ❌ **Inventory** (items CRUD, lots CRUD, movements, alerts)
- ❌ **Finance/Invoices** (create, pay, void, revenue reports, pricing)
- ❌ **Lab Results** (CRUD)
- ❌ **Queue** (today, call, skip, assign-room, start-consultation, complete)
- ❌ **Public Content** (home, news, departments, doctors)
- ❌ **Edge cases**: duplicate booking, slot conflict, invalid UUID, pagination, etc.

---

## 3. Implementation Phases

### Phase 1: Shared Test Infrastructure (Base Class)
Create `AbstractIntegrationTest` to eliminate boilerplate across test files.

### Phase 2: Public Endpoints (No Auth Required)
- `GET /api/v1/content/home`
- `GET /api/v1/news`  
- `GET /api/v1/departments`
- `GET /api/v1/doctors`

### Phase 3: Patient Auth & Portal
- `POST /api/v1/patient-auth/claim`
- `POST /api/v1/patient-auth/login`
- `POST /api/v1/patient-auth/refresh`
- `POST /api/v1/patient-auth/logout`
- Patient portal: overview, appointments, lab-results, messages, profile, profile update

### Phase 4: Admin Endpoints
- Admin Users: list, get, create, update, delete, activate, deactivate, role change
- Admin Departments: list, get, create, update, delete, assign-doctor, remove-doctor
- Admin Rooms: list, get, create, update, status, delete  
- Admin Schedule: templates, time slots, special closures
- Admin Stats, Monitoring, Audit Logs

### Phase 5: Finance & Inventory
- Invoices: list, create, pay, void
- Pricing: list, create, update
- Revenue Reports: daily, monthly
- Inventory Items: list, create, update, delete
- Inventory Lots: list, create, update
- Inventory Movements: list, create
- Inventory Alerts

### Phase 6: Queue & Lab Results
- Queue: today, call, skip, assign-room, start-consultation, complete
- Lab Results: create, get, list by appointment, delete

### Phase 7: Edge Cases & Data Validation
- Duplicate booking same slot
- Invalid UUID formats
- Empty/missing required fields
- Boundary values (dates in past, overlapping slots)
- Pagination edge cases (page out of range)
- Concurrent status transitions
- Cross-role authorization violations
- SQL injection attempts in search params

### Phase 8: Enhanced Sample Data
- Ensure all seed data covers realistic scenarios
- Add edge-case seed data for testing

---

