## 5. Edge Cases Per Domain

### Authentication
- Login with non-existent email
- Login with empty body
- Login with SQL injection in email
- Refresh with expired refresh token
- Refresh with invalid cookie
- Logout without being logged in

### Appointments/Booking
- Book with past date
- Book with duplicate slot (already booked)
- Book with non-existent doctor
- Book with invalid CCCD format
- Cancel already-cancelled appointment
- Status transition: CONFIRMED → DONE (should fail, must go through workflow)

### Admin
- Create user with duplicate email
- Delete the last admin (should prevent?)
- Assign doctor to non-existent department
- Create department with duplicate name
- Update non-existent user/department/room

### Inventory
- Create item with negative quantity
- Movement that would make stock negative
- Lot with past expiration date
- Delete item that has active lots

### Finance
- Create invoice for non-existent appointment
- Pay already-paid invoice
- Void already-voided invoice
- Revenue report for future date
- Revenue report for date with no data

### Patient Portal
- Access with staff token (should fail)
- Update profile with invalid data
- Access non-existent patient resources

---

